{"tid":666466,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎傾下何謂\"孝\"?","createTime":"2018-05-16T01:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T02:47:05.000Z","uid":182067,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5c25c0553431192a878f158b2160aa2a4038fb","tid":666466,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"話說主角已經搬左出黎住,有老婆仲生左個仔。<br />\n<br />\n星期二朝早收到老母個電話，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =老母,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =主角<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :今晚上去你到食飯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :好呀，我買哂餸,你咩都唔使買，直接上黎食就OK。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :得啦,無問題!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我屋企真係咩都有架啦,,,,唔好買野上黎，有菜有肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係啦,,我飲完茶就上黎。<br />\n<br />\n忙完一日,,,,,帶住疲憊既身軀番到屋企，一開門,見老婆面有難色，心知不妙，一入廚房，一盒叉燒，有一煲豬手(肯定夠6個人食)，浸左2斤以上既菜，仲有一大煲湯，但今晚得4個人食。。。。(雪櫃加多一碟肉餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,卑你聽日食)<br />\n<br />\n我的計劃全部沒有了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一早準備好哂既肉同菜,,,,又要放多日??? (事實係唔可以再放,掉掉掉) <br />\n<br />\n我個刻真係好嬲,,,,嬲到冇哂反應。<br />\n<br />\n我開始煮頭先佢帶個的餸,,,,,,,煮既過程,,,,,思考緊何謂孝? 孝就係永遠聽呀爸媽講,不能反對,只可以順應佢地既計劃? 佢地個的就係計劃,我個的就唔係?<br />\n<br />\n默默地食完餐飯，送左佢走，條氣依然唔順，睇唔開，成晚都訓唔到。無錯，因為我同老母個性格係一樣，我地各自有自己既計劃，只要set 左就要跟住行，有強迫症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n老母根本就係要擺出一幅無得輪既樣子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我特登買餸,山長水遠送到上黎，食啦,對你好呀。<br />\n<br />\n我一控制唔到就會好嬲(屈埋係個心到...)。我諗老母一樣，佢或者某的人會話:我/佢出發點係為你好!!!!! 驚你冇野食，食唔飽，會餓死呀! 買埋餸上黎你仲想點? 冇湯水飲會死人架!<br />\n<br />\n但我都有我既計劃，點解要一次又一次咁破壞我既計劃。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預左開得呢的post 一定卑人屌,,,有個老母對你咁好執到啦,仲嘈!!!! 佢仲可以整到幾多餐卑你呀! 老母大過天,不孝! 我明老母咁做係想我好,,,但可否先溝通?<br />\n<br />\n完,都係呻下姐...繼續番工。"},{"pid":"e8a5289de343e543589a4023b7d7db3216ef633d","tid":666466,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea16830f034f075ea33e7b306453d2d0fb3aa3f","tid":666466,"uid":72562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T01:55:32.000Z","msg":"佢走左之後掉哂佢買既野食 <br />\n煮自己個d<br />\n<br />\n利申唔知咩係孝"},{"pid":"92e48cddbeef33e6404a908e6ca68fef6eee0521","tid":666466,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"假膠味甚濃"},{"pid":"214f90437c182dd9ddb3f0794f47890720d69d25","tid":666466,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"我估計係老母知你煮既野唔食得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以佢先用咁婉轉既方式勸你收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b90f12f9e409b8b529dfb8e365da09e3213ed9a","tid":666466,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"想知樓主老母係咪一早買好餸先打電話比樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aef9d6090944342e39a232d9c8c7925bd87faf2","tid":666466,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e48cddbeef33e6404a908e6ca68fef6eee0521","tid":666466,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"假膠味甚濃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d254904302bddec737c259c01ca30df58589a2a","tid":666466,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aef9d6090944342e39a232d9c8c7925bd87faf2","tid":666466,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p